APInbox,allows,users,to,interact,with,a,web,app,via,email,without,adding,any,email,polling,code,APInbox,gives,users,a,special,email,address,that,instantly,translates,incoming,emails,into,form,submissions,that,are,pushed,in,realtime,to,a,web,app,The,API,uses,HTTP,POST,protocol,and,responses,can,be,formatted,in,JSON